  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In the `ThrottlingSyncSource` we're supposed to consider the `peerRateLimit` more accurately:\nCurrently we just check if `wantToRequestObjects(count.longValue()) > 0` and proceed with the request.\nA more accurate behaviour would be to respond with `min(count, wantToRequestObjects(count.longValue()))`",
